text:
Add an `overflow: auto` to the container, like this:

    #container {
         border: 1px red solid;
         overflow: auto;
    }

[You can test the effect here][1], and find [a very good description of how it works here][2].


  [1]: http://jsfiddle.net/nick_craver/febyT/
  [2]: http://www.quirksmode.org/css/clearing.html
